
|WKBUsage: |YKB'buffs'|YKO or |YKB'clearbuff'

    buffs     |WKB- |YKOLists your active buffs.
                * Not all buffs are visible to the system.

    |YKBclearbuff |WKB- |YKOAllows you to remove one of your current buffs.
                The |YKB' clearbuff all' |YKOoption removes all buffs.

    Debuffs, such as curses, hexes, or lingering poisons, appear under
    their own header in |YKB'buffs'|YKO. They cannot be removed with
    |YKB'clearbuff'|YKO. Debuffs expire on their own, or via cures and
    dispels designed for them. Wizards may use |YKB'dispelall'|YKO for
    stuck debuffs.

    An active parasite appears at the end of |YKB'buffs'|YKO with its real
    remaining online time and starvation state. Parasites are not normal
    buffs and cannot be removed with |YKB'clearbuff'|YKO. Use
    |YKB'parasite'|YKO for full details or |YKB'purge parasite'|YKO to remove one.

